        .columns-group
          .one_half
            figure(data-animate)
              a.image-link(href='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-half.jpg')
                img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg' alt='Image Title')
              figcaption Caption
          .one_half
            figure(data-animate)
              a.image-link(href='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-half.jpg')
                img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg' alt='Image Title')
              figcaption Caption
      
      
      
      //- Row: Centered large quote text (heading-1)
      //- Row
      section.content-row.full.row_padding_left.row_padding_right.dark-section(data-bgcolor='#111')
        .columns-group
          .one_full
            hr
            hr
            h3.heading-1.has-mask.text-align-center.no-margins(data-play-once='')
              | For Neo Systems it meant starting from the object, letting form drive every visual decision made.
            hr
      //- Row
      section.content-row.full.row_padding_top.row_padding_bottom.row_padding_left.row_padding_right.dark-section(data-bgcolor='#111')
        .columns-group
          .one_full
            .clapat-slider-wrapper.content-slider.small-looped-carousel.autocenter.animated-entry
              .clapat-slider
                .clapat-slider-viewport
                  .clapat-slide
                    .slide-img
                      img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-half.jpg' alt='Image Title')
                  .clapat-slide
                    .slide-img
                      img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-half.jpg' alt='Image Title')
                  .clapat-slide
                    .slide-img
                      img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg' alt='Image Title')
                  .clapat-slide
                    .slide-img
                      img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-half.jpg' alt='Image Title')
              .clapat-controls
                .clapat-button-prev.slider-button-prev
                .clapat-button-next.slider-button-next
                .clapat-slider-pagination
      //- /Row



                
      //- Row: Two right-offset text columns (2/4 spacer + 1/4 + 1/4)
      section.content-row.full.row_padding_left.row_padding_right.dark-section(data-bgcolor='#111')
        .columns-group
          .two_fourth
          .one_fourth
            p.has-mask(data-play-once) Neo needed a clear position in a crowded market. Not the rugged adventurer, not the technical pro. A camera for people who care as much about design as they do about what they capture.
          .one_fourth
            p.has-mask(data-play-once) CGI direction focused on restraint. Every frame was built around the product alone, no props, no context added. The geometry of the cube did the work, shadow and light told the rest.
      section.content-row.full.row_padding_top.row_padding_bottom.row_padding_left.row_padding_right.dark-section(data-bgcolor='#111')
        .columns-group
          .one_half
            figure(data-animate)
              a.image-link(href='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg')
                img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg' alt='Image Title')
              figcaption Caption
          .one_half
            figure(data-animate)
              a.image-link(href='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg')
                img(src='../images/projects/temp/temp-image-full.jpg' alt='Image Title')
              figcaption Caption
        .columns-group
          .one_full
            hr
    //- Project Navigation — next project transition
    section#project-nav.flip-title-onload(data-next-bgcolor='#0c0c0c')
      #project-nav-wrapper
        #project-nav-caption.content-full-width.text-align-center
          .wrapper
            a.next-ajax-link-project(data-type='page-transition' href='project02.html' data-ball='hover' data-ball-type='blur' data-ball-color='#b880ff' data-ball-size='small' data-ball-radius='rounded' data-ball-info='fa-solid fa-arrow-right' data-ball-info-color='#000')
            .inner
